{"tid":1930114,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"50 多款熱門 APP 遭爆利用 iOS 安全漏洞偷看「複製貼上」內容！","createTime":"2020-03-17T10:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T04:18:36.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"087372499b75df9be2ad6ee427b7ac330a2745df","tid":1930114,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"蘋果再傳資安危機，如果你也常使用「複製貼上」功能，你使用的內容可能已經被看光光！根據《MacRumors》報導，資安專家發現iOS 13.3中，有漏洞讓App能不經同意窺探使用者複製的文字內容，可能因此讓密碼或機密資訊外洩。目前已發現50款應用程式使用該漏洞，其中包括TikTok抖音、微博、Viber、<a href=\"http://Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHotels.com&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB1tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=ec2ba9cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Hotels.com</a>、紐約時報等知名App。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/03/04/99/7549924.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=465\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F03%2F04%2F99%2F7549924.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D465&h=7cf86fd3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n根據Talal Haj Bakry和 Tommy Mysk的調查報告，這個漏洞來自iOS 、iPadOS在使用權限上，並<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有特別限制App取用剪貼簿的內容。</span></span></em>他們也發現許多熱門App都有使用這個漏洞，類別包含遊戲、社交軟體、新聞等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7098/4420272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7098%2F4420272&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB1tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=70effdb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7098/4420272</a>"},{"pid":"ec5f3191a4c07330405b52777773a7e12a0718a7","tid":1930114,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:44:33.000Z","msg":"這些App會在啟動時查看剪貼簿內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，少則會多次查看；大部分都只有使用文字類型的內容、而非圖片或pdf文件。目前還不清楚這些被偷看內容被如何使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。專家呼籲蘋果儘速採取行動補上漏洞，蘋果方面目前則還沒有回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"06bfd445a3d67b6538ea61ccc277a4e0751d33af","tid":1930114,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"偷password"},{"pid":"f8fc2bd6d701163aab0796bcb6660bac45523675","tid":1930114,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:47:29.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 d password..."},{"pid":"e9b5836c5ecf925643cacc21bb3855b9ea3fbc27","tid":1930114,"uid":71508,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"Oh shit<br />\nThey steal my av link"},{"pid":"5f89249f75e3d89e59847d6efce8fd8878afc20c","tid":1930114,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母車牌都偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2581bb052d8523307081ed33248baf75219ad7b4","tid":1930114,"uid":233817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"唔知13.4 有無fix 到"},{"pid":"eb90312de4d26a63e503f1c5e3af9b8fd1e1baf8","tid":1930114,"uid":26333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"Ios12又win<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd079ee6f78470ff564ea05529b9e3e6df022f9e","tid":1930114,"uid":81113,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:01:42.000Z","msg":"邊個走去copy and paste password咁撚叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s