ime":"2020-03-17T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"【世衛兩員工確診 曾到總部上班】<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織有兩名職員確診武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n世衛發言人指，該兩名職員辦公後如常歸家，並於家中出現病徵，隨後雙雙確診武漢肺炎。暫時未知有關職員是否於應變小組中工作。<br />\n<br />\n世衛總部有大約2400名員工，但為減少傳播機會，大部份員工已經被安排在家工作。而世衛總部所在的瑞士，至今已經有超過2200宗確診個案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dbc.131/photos/a.122771689139239/195762545173486/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdbc.131%2Fphotos%2Fa.122771689139239%2F195762545173486%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB1tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=c1a30a09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dbc.131/photos/a.122771689139239/195762545173486/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"f331d9c1b158bd8192e19a6d2888747630d4c9d1","tid":1930114,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fb662f0cf976b70c8cb492ecda02084ce453e2c","tid":1930114,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"以下開放大家Ctrl + v"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:10:52.000Z","msg":"293514"},{"pid":"0079fc9a034acf97616a53c639d5ec8cbeacb05c","tid":1930114,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65a48ea0c41198650f640705de5124be1d33306c","tid":1930114,"uid":335303,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3fb662f0cf976b70c8cb492ecda02084ce453e2c","tid":1930114,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"以下開放大家Ctrl + v"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"最近破咗 真係試過好多次先成功<br />\n我嘅經驗係條撚慢慢插入 唔可以一下就插入去<br />\n頭幾次女下就淨係插到半條<br />\n最近一次就女上 終於成功成條插入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"變左gay post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bdc22759a34d9936891c8ae8cd86bd35712f84","tid":1930114,"uid":1130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"偷囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx